{"tid":1901984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港警民比例世界稱冠，今年打算再突破自己。","createTime":"2020-02-28T06:09:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T07:03:06.000Z","uid":261647,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a15846558b656fcdea139a1fae3f78a7264dcf21","tid":1901984,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T06:09:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/zeno.lung/posts/2678661009036677\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fzeno.lung%2Fposts%2F2678661009036677&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0U9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=b117bb70\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/zeno.lung/posts/2678661009036677</a><br />\n<br />\n香港警民比例世界稱冠，今年打算再突破自己。聯合國毒品和犯罪問題辦事處2013年資料，香港每10萬人有450.7名警察。香港警務處網頁，2018年有警察39899名。香港統計處網頁，2019年香港人口7500.7千人。警民比例531.9。2020年政府財政預算增聘2543警。警民比例565.8，超越俄羅斯。（仆街第一都係第一）"},{"pid":"70453e91806ff9ffd65322532a0183e2d0d238e3","tid":1901984,"uid":134415,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T06:11:09.000Z","msg":"police state唔係得個名"},{"pid":"e7a7bab7e78aea7dda49d0d9b2248e0002b767a2","tid":1901984,"uid":808,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T06:12:32.000Z","msg":"你信唔信來緊會請大陸人做POPO"},{"pid":"9ee90790eccdc0156a9498dead8e6cd1bb422371","tid":1901984,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T06:13:17.000Z","msg":"<del>亞洲</del>世界第一"},{"pid":"d18c0d31f95124f34d470a7750aef6456b17ce87","tid":1901984,"uid":308482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T06:13:33.000Z","msg":"G持，拒絕溫水煮蛙支持武力鎮壓"},{"pid":"fd5b3e9008e334e342f282e082c210b281f39ac3","tid":1901984,"uid":229369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e7a7bab7e78aea7dda49d0d9b2248e0002b767a2","tid":1901984,"uid":808,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T06:12:32.000Z","msg":"你信唔信來緊會請大陸人做POPO"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T06:13:45.000Z","msg":"你點知我哋計劃的"},{"pid":"29b8805